<section id="projects" class="projects-section">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Featured Projects</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Embedded Systems to AI Solutions</p>
    </header>

    <div class="bento-grid">
      <!-- P1: Large Item -->
      <div class="bento-item p1" onclick="openModal('p1')">
        <div class="glass-panel card-inner">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="tag">STM32 Embedded</span>
            <h3>산업용 세탁기 제어</h3>
            <p>상태머신(FSM) 기반의 공정 제어 시스템 설계. 타이머 인터럽트를 활용한 정밀 급수/세탁 제어.</p>
            <div class="tech-stack">
              <span>C</span><span>STM32</span><span>State Machine</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-industry"></i></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- P3: Medium Item -->
      <div class="bento-item p3" onclick="openModal('p3')">
        <div class="glass-panel card-inner">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="tag">AI Vision</span>
            <h3>SSAFY AI Challenge (VQA)</h3>
            <p>Qwen2.5-VL 파인튜닝으로 VQA 성능 0.76 → 0.94 달성.</p>
            <div class="tech-stack">
              <span>Python</span><span>Qwen</span><span>LoRA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- P2: Medium Item -->
      <div class="bento-item p2" onclick="openModal('p2')">
        <div class="glass-panel card-inner">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="tag">RTOS Logic</span>
            <h3>스마트워치 모의 시스템</h3>
            <p>다중 인터럽트 우선순위 설계를 통한 실시간 처리.</p>
            <div class="tech-stack">
              <span>C</span><span>Interrupts</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- P4: Small Item -->
      <div class="bento-item p4" onclick="openModal('p4')">
        <div class="glass-panel card-inner">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="tag">Data Analysis</span>
            <h3>재난 피해 규모 예측</h3>
            <p>공공데이터 XGBoost 모델링.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- P5: Small Item -->
      <div class="bento-item p5" onclick="openModal('p5')">
        <div class="glass-panel card-inner">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="tag">Backend</span>
            <h3>SelF 이커머스</h3>
            <p>Django/Docker 풀스택 개발.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, white, var(--c-slate-400));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* Bento Grid */
  .bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 300px);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  
  .bento-item { cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
  .bento-item:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }

  /* Grid Areas */
  .p1 { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
  .p3 { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 1; }
  .p2 { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
  .p4 { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
  .p5 { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; } /* Adjusted for flow */

  .card-inner {
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .bento-item:hover .card-inner {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
  }

  .card-content {
    padding: 30px;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .tag {
    color: var(--c-accent-light);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .bento-item h3 {
    margin: 0 0 15px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: white;
  }
  .bento-item p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: auto;
  }
  
  .tech-stack {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .tech-stack span {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--c-slate-300);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  
  .card-icon {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: 0.3s;
  }
  .bento-item:hover .card-icon {
    color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .bento-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: auto;
    }
    .p1 { grid-column: span 2; height: 350px; }
    .p3 { grid-column: span 2; height: 280px; }
    .p2, .p4, .p5 { grid-column: span 1; height: 280px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .p1, .p3, .p2, .p4, .p5 { grid-column: span 1; height: auto; min-height: 250px; }
  }
</style>
